ure termination of RPC calls\n\n**Next Steps Needed:**\nTo confirm the root cause, we would need:\n- Metrics data for recommendationservice and currencyservice during this period\n- Trace data to see the full call chain and identify where the context cancellation occurs\n- Resource utilization metrics for the affected services", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio (0.0 to 8.95) and server_error_ratio (0.0 to 8.95), along with a spike in rrt_max (265051.0 to 60001762.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0 -> 8.95, server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 8.95, rrt_max: 265051.0 -> 60001762.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio (0.0 to 14.4) and server_error_ratio (0.0 to 14.4) observed.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0 -> 14.4, server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 14.4\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated error_ratio (0.0 to 15.13) and server_error_ratio (0.0 to 15.13).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0 -> 15.13, server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 15.13\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"High client_error_ratio (0.0 to 42.86) and error_ratio (0.0 to 42.86).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 42.86, error_ratio: 0.0 -> 42.86\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in rrt_max (21802.0 to 9006.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 21802.0 -> 9006.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio (0.0 to 62.5) and client_error_ratio (0.0 to 62.5).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"e